<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Autocomplete on ilo</title><link>https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/tags/autocomplete/</link><description>Recent content in Autocomplete on ilo</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/tags/autocomplete/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Autocomplete</title><link>https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/usage/autocomplete/</link><pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/usage/autocomplete/</guid><description>&lt;p>The &lt;code>ilo generate-completion&lt;/code> command generates autocompletion configuration for shells such as &lt;a href="https://www.gnu.org/software/bash/">bash&lt;/a> and &lt;a href="https://www.zsh.org/">zsh&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Once enabled you can use the &lt;code>&amp;lt;TAB&amp;gt;&lt;/code> key to autocomplete ilo commands and their options:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-console" data-lang="console">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="gp">#&lt;/span> autocomplete commands
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="gp">$&lt;/span> ilo s&amp;lt;TAB&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="gp">$&lt;/span> ilo shell
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="gp">#&lt;/span> autocomplete options
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="gp">$&lt;/span> ilo shell --re&amp;lt;TAB&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="gp">$&lt;/span> ilo shell --remove-image
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="bash">bash&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>In order to integrate autocompletion into &lt;a href="https://www.gnu.org/software/bash/">bash&lt;/a>, follow these steps:&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>Create or edit &lt;code>~/.bashrc&lt;/code>.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Add the following line
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">source&lt;/span> &amp;lt;&lt;span class="o">(&lt;/span>ilo generate-completion&lt;span class="o">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Reload your shell (or create a new one)&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;h2 id="zsh">zsh&lt;/h2>
